Data Model#

The example defines a three-level hierarchy representing a company structure:

type Person = {
  name: string
  phoneNumber: string
}

type Department = {
  name: string
  staff: Person[]
}

type Company = {
  name: string
  departments: Department[]
}



Sample Data#

